## Calibration Notes

Predict the baseline-normalized composite score. Values above 1.0 beat the
baseline on average, but lopsided per-metric movement is a major risk for this
task. If you predict invalid, set `fitness` to null.

## Output Contract

Write a single file `prediction.json` containing only a JSON object with fields
`valid`, `fitness`, `confidence`, and `reasoning`. Do not write anything else.
